{
  "page": "Sar Mell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Sar Mell</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nRuined city</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> region, <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Destroyed</th><td>\nduring the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sar Mell is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Sar Mell is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 87.2%; left: 75.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sar Mell\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Sar Mell</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of Sar Mell\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Sar Mell</b> is a ruined city of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> that sits on the eastern bank of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> to the north of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> in western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. Almost directly across the river to the west sits the city of <a href=\"/index.php/Volon_Therys\" title=\"Volon Therys\">Volon Therys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sar_Mell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynish_Wars\" title=\"Rhoynish Wars\">Rhoynish Wars</a>, Sar Mell, a pale city known for its flowers, fought with nearby <a href=\"/index.php/Volon_Therys\" title=\"Volon Therys\">Volon Therys</a>, a colony of the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>. Sar Mell was burned during the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Turtle_War\" title=\"First Turtle War\">First Turtle War</a>, while Volon Therys was flooded with Rhoynish <a href=\"/index.php/Water_magic\" title=\"Water magic\">water magic</a>. Sar Mell was ruined during the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a> and its people were enslaved by Valyria.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sar_Mell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Map_of_the_Free_Cities_(A_Dance_with_Dragons)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Map of the Free Cities (A Dance with Dragons)\">Map of the Free Cities</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: Ten Thousand Ships.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible uncollapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Region_Free_Cities\" t